[25:00] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'between different objects much more accurately. So, here\'s how this new SVG model works. It basically removes the VAE component of the diffusion model and instead of the VAE, it uses Dino, which'

[25:12] [scene:talk]
